EVEN TO PEOPLE THAT PREVIOUSLY
MAY HAVE BEEN ATTRACTED

00:58:53.212 --> 00:58:54.514
TO A KIND OF IDEALISM

00:58:54.514 --> 00:58:57.116
THAT WAS ALSO PART
OF THE IDEA OF EUGENICS.

