TO FIX ALMOST ANY PROBLEM.

01:13:12.139 --> 01:13:14.742
AND THE ATTITUDE
OF PSYCHOANALYSIS

01:13:14.742 --> 01:13:19.080
THAT ULTIMATELY EVERY DIFFICULTY
COULD BE UNDERSTOOD

01:13:19.080 --> 01:13:22.550
SEEN AS MEANINGFUL AND
POTENTIALLY, AT LEAST, CHANGED

01:13:22.550 --> 01:13:25.586
WAS SOMETHING THAT WAS
VERY APPEALING TO AMERICANS.

01:13:25.586 --> 01:13:29.056
Osgood:
FREUD ORIGINALLY DESIGNED
PSYCHOANALYSIS

01:13:29.056 --> 01:13:31.225
