01:13:31.225 --> 01:13:38.165
ESSENTIALLY NORMAL PEOPLE
DISABLED BY INNER CONFLICTS.

01:13:38.165 --> 01:13:41.996
BUT HIS AMERICAN DISCIPLES
HERWISE.

01:13:44.672 --> 01:13:46.841
ONE OF THE QUESTIONS
OF THE 1950s

01:13:46.841 --> 01:13:49.443
WAS HOW POWERFUL WOULD
PSYCHOANALYSIS BE

01:13:49.443 --> 01:13:51.612
AS AN INTERVENTION,
AS A THERAPY?

01:13:51.612 --> 01:13:55.082
WAS IT ONLY GOING TO BE
A THERAPY FOR THE WORRIED-WELL

01:13:55.082 --> 01:13:57.685
FOR THE MILDLY NEUROTIC,
FOR THE ANXIOUS?

01:13:57.685 --> 01:14:00.721
