01:14:00.721 --> 01:14:03.758
TO HELP THE MOST BRUTALLY
MENTALLY ILL OF OUR SOCIETY

01:14:03.758 --> 01:14:05.059
THE SCHIZOPHRENICS?

01:14:07.662 --> 01:14:10.698
Osgood:
ONE OF THE PSYCHOANALYSTS
WHO BELIEVES IT CAN

01:14:10.698 --> 01:14:13.301
IS FRIEDA FROMM-REICHMANN.

