THEIR TEETH ARE PULLED;

01:22:20.854 --> 01:22:26.059
THEIR BLOOD IS LET;
THEIR BRAINS ARE SLICED.

01:22:26.059 --> 01:22:29.096
BUT THE PROBLEM OF TREATING
THE DESPERATELY ILL

01:22:29.096 --> 01:22:31.265
DOES NOT ABATE.

01:22:31.265 --> 01:22:33.433
NEITHER SIDE
IN THE ONGOING BATTLE--

01:22:33.433 --> 01:22:36.904
