AND I SAID

01:23:23.750 --> 01:23:27.221
"WELL, IT WON'T BE A PILL, BUT
SOMEHOW WE'LL PROBABLY LEARN

01:23:27.221 --> 01:23:29.389
HOW TO DO BETTER
THAN WE DO NOW."

01:23:29.389 --> 01:23:31.558
BUT, YOU KNOW,
IT SEEMED TO BE RIDICULOUS.

01:23:33.293 --> 01:23:35.896
Osgood:
