01:23:43.704 --> 01:23:45.005
AN ACCIDENTAL DISCOVERY

01:23:45.005 --> 01:23:48.041
LEADS TO RESEARCH
ON A RADICALLY NEW TREATMENT

01:23:48.041 --> 01:23:51.511
A TREATMENT THAT MIGHT NOT ONLY
GIVE NEW HOPE TO PATIENTS

01:23:51.511 --> 01:23:53.247
BUT ALSO REVOLUTIONIZE

01:23:53.247 --> 01:23:55.849
THE WAY PSYCHIATRY LOOKS
AT MENTAL ILLNESS.

01:23:55.849 --> 01:23:58.886
IT BEGINS WITH A SURGEON
NAMED HENRI LABORIT

01:23:59.319 --> 01:24:01.054
IN SEARCH OF A MEDICATION

01:24:01.054 --> 01:24:04.091
THAT WILL CALM HIS PATIENTS
BEFORE SURGERY.

01:24:04.524 --> 01:24:09.296
HE ADAPTS AN EXISTING COMPOUND
BY ADDING AN ANTIHISTAMINE.

01:24:10.597 --> 01:24:14.501
HE FINDS THAT THE NEW DRUG,
CALLED CHLORPROMAZINE

01:24:14.501 --> 01:24:18.405
OR LARGACTIL,
